data.description: Charming one-and-a-half-story residence, adorned with original hardwood flooring and woodwork that radiates character and meticulous craftsmanship. A sun-soaked sunroom, adorned with elegant French doors, invites you to indulge in relaxation and unwind in absolute style. The upper-level expansion enhances the versatility of this impeccably kept dwelling, rendering it a superb choice for both first-time homebuyers and astute investors. Immerse yourself in the seamless fusion of vintage allure and contemporary comfort found within this welcoming home, poised and ready for you to personalize and call your own.
